A CRAFT beer festival takes place in Glasgow this weekend. It's cheers for beer festival A CRAFT beer festival takes place in Glasgow this weekend.The Craft Beer Rising, at Drygate brewery, starts at 6pm on Friday.The event is being billed as the UK's first experimental craft brewery and around 3000 people are expected to attend.There will be up to 200 beers from 40 global craft breweries, also known as microbreweries. 